OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FSheffield City Council faces a school
OL,7,Frepairs backlog worth around #100M,
OL,8,FITV Calendar News can reveal.
OL,10,FAn ITV News Freedom of Information
OL,11,Frequest has revealed that every one of
OL,12,Fthe 64 schools maintained by Sheffield
OL,13,FCity Council requires some degree of
OL,14,Frepair, with the total cost for the
OL,15,Fcity's maintenance backlog hitting
OL,16,F#100 million.
OL,18,FOne of those schools is Carterknowle
OL,19,FJuniors, which was forced to evacuate
OL,20,Flast month after a section of its
OL,21,Fceiling collapsed in a classroom.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
