FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FParents of the more than 230 pupils
OL,7,Fwere told to collect their children
OL,8,Fwhilst emergency repairs took place.
OL,10,FThe school's Headteacher Lucy Atherton
OL,11,Fsaid: "In September, part of the
OL,12,Fceiling fell down in the staff room.
OL,13,FWe contacted the council, and they
OL,14,Fcame and told us we would need to have
OL,15,Fthe tiles fixed on the roof, which we
OL,16,Fhave had done.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,F"The ceiling that fell down fell down
OL,7,Fon top of some chairs where the staff
OL,8,Fhad been sitting moments before, so
OL,9,Fthat was a real concern to make sure
OL,10,Fthat everyone was safe.
OL,12,F"Since then, we had another ceiling
OL,13,Fcollapse where some of the tiles in
OL,14,Fthe lowered ceiling fell down in one
OL,15,Fof the classrooms. That was the point
OL,16,Fwe really felt we had to ask the
OL,17,Fcouncil to do something.
OL,19,F"It's been an ongoing concern for many
OL,20,Fyears with the roof leaking."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FThe school, built in 1904, has a
OL,7,Fstatus as a Grade II listed, which
OL,8,FAtherton said adds complexity and cost
OL,9,Fto it's maintenance.
OL,11,FAtherton said: "The Grade II listing
OL,12,Fof the building is the problem for us.
OL,13,FIt requires specialists to come in and
OL,14,Fmake sure everything we are doing is
OL,15,Fokay. A window we had mended cost over
OL,16,F#5,000, as it had to be made by hand
OL,17,Fto meet those requirements."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FSimon Christie, Vice-Chair of
OL,7,FGovernors for Carterknowle Junior
OL,8,FSchool, said: "You can't really walk
OL,9,Faround the school without seeing
OL,10,Fsomewhere that needs remedial work.
OL,11,FIt's a beautiful building from the
OL,12,Foutside, but the fundamental fact is,
OL,13,Fit's not a fit location for the
OL,14,Feducation of children.
OL,16,F"We cannot still be using this as a
OL,17,Fschool in five, ten, or fifteen years
OL,18,Ftime. The building isn't going to
OL,19,Fmagically heal itself. We need a
OL,20,Flonger-term solution."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Duncan Strafford, a parent
OL,7,Fat the school, said he is "disgusted".
OL,9,F"This school has had years of leaking
OL,10,Froofs and years of neglect," he said.
OL,11,F"They've left it to the last minute -
OL,12,Funtil the ceiling of the school
OL,13,Fchildren go to (collapsed). It's
OL,14,Fabsolute disgust, absolute
OL,15,Fdevastation. I don't send my kids to
OL,16,Fschool so they can work in an unsafe
OL,17,Flocation."
OL,19,FHe added: "A ceiling doesn't just
OL,20,Fcollapse one day - it's a series of
OL,21,Fevents that have been ignored."
OL,26,@uD@PpmuD@Zpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
