CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FA month on from the schools temporary
OL,7,Fclosure, it has several areas of the
OL,8,Fplayground fenced off, with
OL,9,Fscaffolding on both sides of the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,FHeadteacher Atherton said: "Lots of
OL,13,Fthe school yard is fenced off. That
OL,14,Fhas an impact because one year group
OL,15,Fhas to be inside while the other is
OL,16,Foutside; navigating that is quite
OL,17,Ftricky for the children.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,F"It also has a big impact on their
OL,7,Fwellbeing, because they want to be
OL,8,Foutside to run off the energy they've
OL,9,Fsaved up in the morning."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Sheffield City Council
OL,12,Fsaid: "Council commissioned an
OL,13,Findependent external firm of surveyors
OL,14,Fto attend and recommend potential
OL,15,Fremedial works. All suggested measures
OL,16,Ffrom that survey were put in place as
OL,17,Frecommended.
OL,19,F"We are continuing to use all means we
OL,20,Fcan to support the school going
OL,21,Fforward."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772547083
OL,3,CSheffield faces #100m backlog in
OL,4,Cschool repairs
OL,6,FIt added: "Like many local authorities
OL,7,Facross the country, Sheffield faces
OL,8,Fsignificant pressures in maintaining
OL,9,Fan ageing school estate.
OL,11,F"Current funding levels allow us to
OL,12,Faddress only a small proportion of
OL,13,Fidentified need each year. As a
OL,14,Fresult, we need to consistently
OL,15,Fprioritise and review allocations from
OL,16,FGovernment for this purpose."
OL,18,FThe Department of Education has been
OL,19,Fapproached for comment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
